Package com.github.themrmilchmann.mjl.events

Class EventBus.Subscriber

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.themrmilchmann.mjl.events.EventBus.Subscriber
  • Enclosing class:
    EventBus
    public static final class EventBus.Subscriber
extends java.lang.Object
    A wrapper class for a subscriber method.

    This class provides several methods that serve as proxies to the underlying subscriber method and may be used by a dispatcher to make decisions about the execution order.

    Since:
    1.0.0

      • dispatch

        public void dispatch​(Event event)
        Dispatches the given Event to the wrapped subscriber.

        The blocking behaviour of this method depends on the executor implementation of the EventBus that the subscriber is registered to.

        Parameters:
        event - the event to dispatch
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if the given event is null
        Since:
        1.0.0
